{"article_id":"lO7Nj8lKFImgAsPk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senators from both parties signaled Sunday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that universal background checks could be the next gun measure","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to get shoved toward the legislative scrap heap or significantly watered down .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Sen. Charles E. Schumer ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"whose bill","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"to expand background checks","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"to cover virtually all gun transactions ,","depth":13},{"id":7,"text":"including private sales ,","depth":13},{"id":8,"text":"has cleared the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"he is nevertheless hunting for a compromise on the issue .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" I ' m working very hard with both Democrats and Republicans , pro-NRA and anti-NRA people ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"to come up with a background check bill","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that will be acceptable to 60 senators","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"and be very strong","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"and get the job done , \"","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"the New York Democrat said on NBC ' s \" Meet the Press.","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"\" \" It ' s very hard .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"We ' re working hard ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and I ' m very hopeful","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that we can get this passed . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Two Republican senators","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"who are backing legislation","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to clarify the definition of people","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"adjudicated mentally ill","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"who are not allowed to own or purchase guns","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"appeared skeptical","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that Mr. Schumer ' s measure could pass the Senate as written .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake of Arizona called universal checks \" a bridge too far for most of us . \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" Well , the paperwork requirements alone would be significant ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"even if there are exemptions for a father","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"passing on a gun to his son or daughter ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"you ' d still have issues with people in a private setting","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"transferring or loaning a gun for somebody , \"","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Mr. Flake said later on the program .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake :","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Universal background checks ' a bridge too far '","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham of South Carolina said","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that out of about 80,000 people","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"who failed background checks last year ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"just 66 were prosecuted .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"\" Why in the world would you expand that system","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"if you ' re not enforcing the law","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that exists today","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"to include private transfers ? \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Graham said on CNN ' s \" State of the Union. \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"\" So I think","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that legislation is going nowhere .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"But I would like to have a robust debate","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"about improving the system","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"to make sure","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that people","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"who are mentally ill","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"do not get a gun","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"to begin with .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"And there ' s a lot","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"we could do in a bipartisan fashion . \"","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"A month after 20 children and six adults were shot to death at Sandy Hook Elementary School in Newtown , Conn. ,","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"President Obama rolled out a package of gun control proposals","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"that included bans on so-called assault weapons and high-capacity magazines as well as near-universal background checks on all gun sales .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid , Nevada Democrat , opted to leave the weapons and magazine bans out of the \" base bill \"","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"he plans to bring to the floor after Congress ' two-week Easter break .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"the weapons ban could not get the 60 votes","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"needed to overcome a potential filibuster","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and get the entire package to the floor .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Reid did say","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that he would ensure senators the opportunity","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"to introduce the bans as amendments .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" In order to be effective ,","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"any bill","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that passes the Senate","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"must include background checks , \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Bipartisan talks","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"involving Mr. Schumer and several others","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"reached an impasse over the issue of record keeping on gun sales ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"so Mr. Schumer went ahead with his own bill .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal , Connecticut Democrat and a member of the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that passed Mr. Schumer ' s measure on a party-line vote ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"said Sunday on CNN ' s \" State of the Union \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"that there is \" room for compromise \" on the issue .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Currently , all sales by licensed firearms dealers must go through background checks ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"but transactions between private individuals do not .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Lawmakers are looking for a way","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"to extend checks to almost all transactions","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"without creating a record-keeping system","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"gun rights supporters fear","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"could turn into a gun registry .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Host Candy Crowley asked","depth":3},{"id":93,"text":"whether a gun bill could be considered a success","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"if the proposed weapons and high-capacity magazine bans are rejected","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"and the background check bill is watered down .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"\" Any step","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that saves lives","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"is a step in the right direction , \"","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"said Mr. Blumenthal .","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"\" And the question is not winning or losing here ,","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"but really saving lives ,","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"which the people of Newtown and the victims there and their families ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"I think ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"want to happen , not just for the sake of those victims ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"but also more than 3,000 people have perished since Newtown","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"as a result of gun violence . \"","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"But Mark Kelly , a retired astronaut and husband of former Rep. Gabrielle Giffords , said","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"any bill","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"that does not include a universal background check","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"is \" a mistake. \"","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"His wife was wounded in a shooting spree in Tucson , Ariz. , in January 2011 .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"\" When you use words like gun control ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"you know ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"gun control doesn ' t poll very well ,","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"but we do know","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"that over 90 percent of Americans support a universal background check , \"","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Mr. Kelly said on \" Fox News Sunday. \"","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"\" And there is incredible momentum in Congress and around the nation","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"to get this done . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":239,"left":211,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":178,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":155,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":122,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":121,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":139,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":129,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":128,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":3,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":4,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":5,"right":123,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":136,"right":137,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":134,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":11,"right":132,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":12,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N